YELLOW FEVER - NIGERIA: CONFIRMED
*********************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
See Also
Yellow fever - Nigeria (north): RFI 20000517221639
Date: Fri, 19 May 2000 12:00:09 -0400
From: Marjorie P. Pollack <pollackmp@mindspring.com>
Source: WHO/CSR

<http://www.who.int/emc/outbreak_news/n2000/may/19may.html>
The Federal Ministry of Health has confirmed 2 cases of yellow fever in
Kano State.
In collaboration with WHO, UNICEF and Medecins sans Frontieres, the
Ministry is planning to conduct a mass vaccination campaign in the affected
areas of Kano State and Ekiti State.
